        <mxCell id="corr-explain" value="The Correlation ID is essential for matching requests with responses:&#xa;&#xa;â€¢ Client generates unique ID (UUID) for each request&#xa;â€¢ ID included in request message header&#xa;â€¢ Server copies ID to response message&#xa;â€¢ Client uses ID to match response to original request&#xa;â€¢ Enables multiple concurrent requests" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;spacingLeft=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
